      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUST DOUG (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (20.49) at this track. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Can measure up this time. NITRO SLIM (8) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 20.17 beating Big Buckets. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Leading chance again. DAD'S BOYS (5) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Robell Clyde (20.32) in a Mix 2/3. Has the pace to be prominent. Has good early speed so he should be prominent despite the squeeze draw. Winning chance. PANAMA ROAD (2) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
